Elizabeth Arden, Inc. (USA)



Published: April 1, 2015
Content info: 165 Pages














Description

This report presents quick facts about Elizabeth Arden, Inc., which is principally involved in Manufacture and Distribution of Prestige Beauty Products (Fragrance, Skin Care and Cosmetics). Illustrated with 161 tables, the report showcases the company's sales performance, key markets and market position as against its competitors operating in the industry.



