Elizabeth Arden, Inc. - Wikipedia






















 






Elizabeth Arden, Inc.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Elizabeth Arden, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: RDEN[1] (discontinued)


Founded
1910 (1910)


Founder
Elizabeth Arden


Headquarters
Miramar, Florida, United States



Key people

E. Scott Beattie (Chairman President & CEO)


Products
Cosmetics, skin care, and fragrances


