Additional Information


Product Details
In the spirit of all or nothing, its bold introduction of Blackcurrant Bud, Pear and Lemon brightens to a heart of Peach Blossom, Jasmine and Muguet. The dry down is a grand finale of Vanilla, Moss, Cedar Wood and Patchouli affirming that this sensual floral is the paradigm of today’s confident woman.


Key Ingredients






   Top Notes
  

   Black Currant Bud, Pear, Lemon
  






   Middle Notes
  

  Peach Blossom, Davana LMR1, Muguet, Jasmine
  






   Base Notes
  

   Vanilla, Moss, Cedarwood, Patchouli
  










