Additional Information


Product Details
Introducing a breakthrough in anti-aging makeup. Infused with Idebenone, this exclusive anti-aging complex continuously repairs skin’s appearance day after day for the ultimate in youth renewal. Instantly, skin looks perfected - smooth, firm and naturally radiant. Vitamin C and key anti-aging ingredients correct skin’s appearance for a firmer, clearer look. Moisture-rich hydra-pigments flawlessly even skin tone for luminous skin perfection that lasts all day. Oil free.
For normal to dry skin
Light to medium coverage
Naturally luminous finish

The super fluid liquid foundation creates a naturally luminous complexion with all-day wear. The lightweight formula provides medium coverage, creating a beautiful flawless look. 
PREVAGE® Foundation is so good for your skin that women who slept with it on overnight experienced amazing results: The foundation lasts 24 hours and upon waking up skin was clear and felt fresh, hydrated and comfortable with a healthy glow. 


Clinical Test Results




97%
 of women said the makeup glides on evenly and blends effortlessly.1 


96%
 of women felt the makeup gave them natural looking coverage.1


95%
 of women saw an immediate improvement to skin's overall appearance.1


93%
 of women said it blurs the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles and imperfections. .1 


91%
  of women did not feel like they were wearing any foundation. 1


87%
 of women said their skin looked radiant. 1



Key Ingredients






   Idebenone Ester
  

   Our exclusive antioxidant helps protect skin from oxidative stress and environmental assaults to help minimize the visible signs of aging.
  






   Hydra-Pigments
  

   Encapsulated, moisture-rich pigments meld with the skin creating a shield to help skin retain moisture while delivering precise long-wear color, and blurring imperfections.
  






   Antioxidant Complex
  

   A potent blend of highly effective antioxidants including Idebenone, Thiotane, Ferulic Acid, L-Carnosine and Green Tea Extract that help protect skin from environmental assaults to help minimize visible signs of aging, and keep skin looking healthy and luminous.
  








Applications and Use





1

Prep and Prime: Apply SUPERSTART Skin Renewal Booster, serum, and moisturizer all over face to prepare and hydrate. Apply Flawless Start Instant Perfecting Primer  to blur imperfections, minimize pores, and create a perfect canvas to improve the length of foundation.



2

Apply Foundation: Use Elizabeth Arden Dual End Foundation Brush to apply PREVAGE® Anti-Aging Foundation Broad Spectrum Sunscreen SPF 30 for a flawless application and airbrush effect. Use the smaller end of the brush to perfect areas around the nose, eyes, and mouth. 



3

 Conceal: Use Flawless Finish Maximum Coverage Concealer to correct imperfections and dark circles.



4

Highlight: Sweep Flawless Finish Correcting and Highlighting Perfector where the light hits your face to highlight and add dimensions. Blend product into skin for natural luminosity.



5

 Powder: Apply Flawless Finish Ultra Smooth Pressed Powder as a last step to set foundation and make it last longer. Use a foundation brush to dust lightly all over the face.



PREVAGE® Usage Instructions






