Additional Information


Product Details
OUTSMART VISIBLE AGING WITH PREVAGE® SUPERIOR ANTI-AGING TECHNOLOGY
 — it’s in our DNA

Every day, in cities all over the world, the environment  is visibly aging your skin; in fact, 80% of all signs of skin aging are due to the environment aggressors such as UV rays, pollution and smoke.1 

Recognizing the global epidemic of pollution, Elizabeth Arden introduces the first-of-its-kind invisible skin shield to combine pollution and UV protection with our DNA Enzyme Complex™ to strengthen skin. Sheer, hydrating, invisible protection to help skin look younger, longer.

New 
PREVAGE® City Smart Broad Spectrum SPF 50 Hydrating Shield
+ DNA Enzyme Complex™
+ Anti-Pollution 
+ Antioxidants

STRENGTHENS skin’s natural defenses with a DNA Enzyme Complex™ to support natural repair systems
PROTECTS against skin dulling pollutants with smart polymers to form an invisible skin shield
DEFENDS against 98% of harmful UVB rays with a Broad Spectrum SPF 50 formula containing 100% micronized titanium dioxide and zinc oxide
VISIBLY IMPROVES skin’s condition
MAINTAINS SKIN HEALTH. Formulated with a powerful antioxidant blend to maintain optimal skin health even in the most heavily polluted cities2
Proof… not Promises™






		WHAT'S AGING YOUR SKIN? 







What's Aging Your Skin?
What's Aging Your Skin?

					80% of all skin aging is due to environmental aggressors such as UV rays, pollution, and smoke.1

New PREVAGE® City Smart protects skin against pollution, sun, and visible aging.


 1 Skin aging and its treatment, L.Bauman, Journal of Pathology, 2007





 


Key Ingredients






   Anti-Pollution Shield Technology
(Protects Against Pollution)
  

   Forms an invisible protective barrier to help prevent harmful toxins and pollution particles from penetrating skin. 100% Mineral Broad Spectrum SPF 50 sunscreen (micronized Zinc Oxide and Titanium Dioxide) filters out UVA and UVB rays.
  






Anti-Pollution Complex
(Defends Against Damage)
  

A potent, patent-pending Anti-Pollution Complex is comprised of an exclusive antioxidant blend of Idebenone, Green Tea, Thiotaine, Ferulic Acid and L-Carnosine to neutralize free radical damage caused by pollution and UV exposure, including both oxygen-based and nitrogen-based free radicals.
  






   DNA Enzyme Complex™
(Strengthens Skin)
  

Helps protect against free radical damage and supports skin’s natural repair process against oxidative stress. Skin’s elastin and collagen matrix are protected and its natural recovery process is strengthened resulting in healthier, more resilient skin.
  








SUPER/SMART Steps






PREVAGE® City Smart sheer, hydrating multi-active skin defender is an essential last step in daily skincare regimens, regardless of age, skin type or concern.



1

Boost:  Apply 1 pump of Elizabeth Arden SUPERSTART Skin Renewal Booster onto a cleansed face. Avoid eye area. Use as the first step in your skincare regimen.
  


2

Correct: Apply PREVAGE® Anti-aging Daily Serum over Elizabeth Arden SUPERSTART Skin Renewal Booster.
  


3

Protect: Apply PREVAGE® City Smart evenly to face and neck as the last step in your morning skincare routine regardless of age, skin type, or concern. (If additional hydration is needed you can add your favorite PREVAGE® moisturizer under City Smart).




PREVAGE® City Smart contains a universal tint and optical diffusers that works well with all skin tones and makeup products. Non-comedogenic, paraben free, and dermatologist tested.
  


PREVAGE® Usage Instructions





